              <title>Massively Open Online Courses – the Death of Universities?</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5289</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5289</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>Welcome!&nbsp; This is a flash debate created by our group of #H800 students on the MA ODE Course.&nbsp; I think the title speaks for itself - and we would welcome any opinions from anyone out there!!!</p>]]></description>
          <pubDate>Mon, 11 Apr 2011 12:48:50 +0000</pubDate>
